SEMDL Help Topic: recipes wrong-layer

If `path:` points to sidecar-only metadata, use `meta:` instead.
If `meta:` points to inline-only structure, use `path:` instead.

Examples:
- `ssd set path:A1.label "売上報告書" --dry-run docs/examples/minimal.ssd`
- `ssd set meta:A1.confidence 0.91 --dry-run docs/examples/minimal.ssd`
